{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Element (要素)","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Glossary/Element","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>要素</strong> (element) はウェブページの一部分です。<a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/XML\">XML</a> と <a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/HTML\">HTML</a> では、要素はデータ項目やテキストのかたまりや画像を含んだり、何も含まなかったりします。ふつうは要素は <a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/Attribute\">属性</a> (attributes) つきの開始タグ (an opening tag) と、囲まれたテキストコンテンツと、閉じタグ (a closing tag) を含んでいます。</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"Example: in <p class=&quot;nice&quot;>Hello world!</p>, '<p class=&quot;nice&quot;>' is an opening tag, 'class=&quot;nice&quot;' is an attribute and its value, 'Hello world!' is enclosed text content, and '</p>' is a closing tag.\" src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/7659/anatomy-of-an-html-element.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n\n<p>要素と<a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/Tag\">タグ</a>は同じでは<em>ありません</em>。タグはソースコード内で要素を開始させたり終了させたりするのに対し、要素は <a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/DOM\">DOM</a> 、つまり<a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/Browser\">ブラウザー</a>に表示するドキュメントモデルの一部分です。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Learn/HTML/Introduction_to_HTML/Getting_started\">要素についての詳細</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Web_Components/Using_custom_elements\">Web_Components/Custom_Elements</a></li>\n <li>DOM の中で要素を表現する<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a> インターフェイス</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"要素 (element) はウェブページの一部分です。XML と HTML では、要素はデータ項目やテキストのかたまりや画像を含んだり、何も含まなかったりします。ふつうは要素は 属性 (attributes) つきの開始タグ (an opening tag) と、囲まれたテキストコンテンツと、閉じタグ (a closing tag) を含んでいます。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Element","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Elemento","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Élément","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"요소","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Elemento","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Элемент","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Element（元素）","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"元素","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/glossary/element","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/glossary/element/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Glossary","title":"MDN Web Docs 用語集: ウェブ関連用語の定義"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Glossary/Element","title":"Element (要素)"}],"pageTitle":"Element (要素) - MDN Web Docs 用語集: ウェブ関連用語の定義 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}